      "is_substep": false,
      "step": "Copy and paste the FAM and HEX tags to your wild type and mutant alleles. Pay attention to which tag is which.\n\nFAM tag: GAAGGTGACCAAGTTCATGCT\nHEX tag: GAAGGTCGGAGTCAACGGATT",
